Welcome to AWS EMR Spark ETL Pipeline's documentation!
======================================================

**datadiver-aws-emr** is a Python project for extract data from JSON files stored
in S3 buckets and load into Parquet tables.

.. note::

   This project is part of the `Udacity's Data Engineeering Nanodegree Program <https://www.udacity.com/course/data-engineer-nanodegree--nd027>`_.
